{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01SysReiXaKLo3SLnKUXjVfA","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have comprehensive information. Let me create a detailed summary report of all findings:\n\n## COMPREHENSIVE ANALYSIS: Quarkus-Specific vs Jakarta EE Code in Cargo Tracker\n\nBased on my thorough analysis of all 106 Java source files, configuration files, and test files in the project, here is a complete breakdown:\n\n---\n\n## FILES THAT **NEED CHANGES** (Quarkus-Specific)\n\n### 1. **Persistence/Repository Layer (4 files) - HIGHEST PRIORITY**\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaCargoRepository.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.panache.PanacheRepositoryBase;`\n  - `import io.quarkus.panache.common.Parameters;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - Implements `PanacheRepositoryBase<Cargo, Long>`\n  - Uses Panache query methods: `find(\"#Cargo.findByTrackingId\", Parameters.with(\"trackingId\", trackingId)).singleResult()`\n  - Uses `persist(cargo)` (Panache method)\n  - Uses `getEntityManager()` (from PanacheRepositoryBase)\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Need to inject `@PersistenceContext EntityManager` and use standard JPA queries\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaHandlingEventRepository.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.panache.PanacheRepositoryBase;`\n  - `import io.quarkus.panache.common.Parameters;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - Implements `PanacheRepositoryBase<HandlingEvent, Long>`\n  - Uses Panache query: `find(\"#HandlingEvent.findByTrackingId\", Parameters.with(\"trackingId\", trackingId)).list()`\n  - Uses `persist(event)` (Panache method)\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Need to inject EntityManager and use standard JPA\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaLocationRepository.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.panache.PanacheRepositoryBase;`\n  - `import io.quarkus.panache.common.Parameters;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - Implements `PanacheRepositoryBase<Location, Long>`\n  - Uses Panache query: `find(\"#Location.findByUnLocode\", Parameters.with(\"unLocode\", unLocode)).singleResult()`\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Need to inject EntityManager and use standard JPA\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaVoyageRepository.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.panache.PanacheRepositoryBase;`\n  - `import io.quarkus.panache.common.Parameters;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - Implements `PanacheRepositoryBase<Voyage, Long>`\n  - Uses Panache query: `find(\"#Voyage.findByVoyageNumber\", Parameters.with(\"voyageNumber\", voyageNumber)).singleResult()`\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Need to inject EntityManager and use standard JPA\n\n---\n\n### 2. **JMS Message Consumers (5 files) - HIGH PRIORITY**\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/CargoHandledConsumer.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.runtime.ShutdownEvent;`\n  - `import io.quarkus.runtime.StartupEvent;`\n  - `import org.eclipse.microprofile.config.inject.ConfigProperty;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - `@ConfigProperty(name = \"app.jms.CargoHandledQueue\", defaultValue = \"CargoHandledQueue\")`\n  - `public void onStart(@Observes StartupEvent ev)` - Quarkus lifecycle event\n  - `public void onStop(@Observes ShutdownEvent ev)` - Quarkus lifecycle event\n  - Manual JMS consumer loop using ExecutorService\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** \n  - Replace @ConfigProperty with `@Inject @ConfigProperty` from MicroProfile Config (standard) or use @Resource with application.properties\n  - Replace StartupEvent/ShutdownEvent with `@PostConstruct`/`@PreDestroy` or standard MDB with `@MessageDriven`\n  - Better: convert to standard Message-Driven Bean with `@MessageDriven`, `@ActivationConfigProperty`\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/DeliveredCargoConsumer.java\n- **Quarkus imports:** Same as CargoHandledConsumer\n- **Quarkus usage:** Same pattern as CargoHandledConsumer\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Same as CargoHandledConsumer\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java\n- **Quarkus imports:** Same as CargoHandledConsumer\n- **Quarkus usage:** Same pattern as CargoHandledConsumer\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Same as CargoHandledConsumer\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java\n- **Quarkus imports:** Same as CargoHandledConsumer\n- **Quarkus usage:** Same pattern as CargoHandledConsumer\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Same as CargoHandledConsumer\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__