rkus annotation to initialize eagerly\n  - `@UnlessBuildProfile(\"test\")` - Quarkus-specific profile management\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** \n  - Replace `@Startup` with `@Singleton` + `@Startup` (Jakarta EE has its own @Startup in jakarta.ejb)\n  - Replace `@UnlessBuildProfile(\"test\")` with custom logic or environment variable check\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/test/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/BookingServiceTestDataGenerator.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.runtime.Startup;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - `@Startup`\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Use `@Singleton` + `@jakarta.ejb.Startup` or manual initialization\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Scheduling (1 file) - MEDIUM PRIORITY**\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/UploadDirectoryScanner.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.scheduler.Scheduled;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - `@Scheduled(every = \"2m\")` - Quarkus Scheduler annotation\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Replace with `@Schedule` from jakarta.ejb with cron expression: `@Schedule(hour=\"*\", minute=\"*/2\")`\n\n---\n\n### 6. **UI Layer (1 file) - LOW PRIORITY**\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/mobile/EventLogger.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.panache.common.Sort;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - `List<Voyage> voyages = voyageRepository.listAll(Sort.by(\"voyageNumber\"));` - Panache API\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Replace with standard JPA: `entityManager.createQuery(\"SELECT v FROM Voyage v ORDER BY v.voyageNumber\", Voyage.class).getResultList()`\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Test Files (1 file) - MEDIUM PRIORITY**\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/test/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/BookingServiceTest.java\n- **Quarkus imports:**\n  - `import io.quarkus.test.junit.QuarkusTest;`\n- **Quarkus usage:**\n  - `@QuarkusTest` - Quarkus testing framework\n- **Jakarta EE replacement:** Replace with Arquillian or Testcontainers for Jakarta EE testing\n\n---\n\n## FILES THAT **DON'T NEED CHANGES** (Pure Jakarta EE)\n\nThe following files use only standard Jakarta EE APIs and require NO changes:\n\n### Application Layer (9 files)\n- ApplicationEvents.java - Interface only\n- BookingService.java - Jakarta Validation annotations\n- CargoInspectionService.java - Jakarta Validation\n- HandlingEventService.java - Jakarta Validation\n- DefaultBookingService.java - jakarta.enterprise, jakarta.inject, jakarta.transaction\n- DefaultCargoInspectionService.java - jakarta.enterprise, jakarta.inject, jakarta.transaction\n- DefaultHandlingEventService.java - jakarta.enterprise, jakarta.inject, jakarta.transaction\n- ApplicationSettings.java - jakarta.persistence\n- DateConverter.java - Pure Java (no Jakarta dependencies)\n- InitLoader.java - jakarta.enterprise, jakarta.inject, jakarta.persistence, jakarta.transaction\n- RestConfiguration.java - jakarta.ws.rs\n\n### Domain Model (31+ files)\nAll domain model files use only standard Jakarta Persistence:\n- All files under domain/model/cargo/* (Cargo.java, Delivery.java, Itinerary.java, Leg.java, RouteSpecification.java, TrackingId.java, etc.)\n- All files under domain/model/handling/* (HandlingEvent.java, HandlingEventFactory.java, HandlingHistory.java, etc.)\n- All files under domain/model/location/* (Location.java, SampleLocations.java, UnLocode.java)\n- All files under domain/model/voyage/* (Voyage.java, VoyageNumber.java, SampleVoyages.java, Schedule.java, CarrierMovement.java)\n- All files under domain/shared/* (Specification.java, AbstractSpecification.java, etc.)\n- All files under domain/service/* (RoutingService.java)\n\n### Infrastructure Layer (2 files needing NO change)\n- LoggerProducer.java - jakarta.enterprise.context, jakarta.enterprise.inject\n- CargoUpdated.java - jakarta.inject.Qualifier\n\n### Interface/Web Layer (30+ files)\nAll JSF backing beans and REST services use standard Jakarta APIs:\n- All files under interfaces/booking/web/* (Booking.java, Track.java, CargoDetails.java, ListCargo.java, etc.)\n- All files under interfaces/booking/facade/* (BookingServiceFacade.java, DefaultBookingServiceFacade.java, all DTOs)\n- All files under interfaces/booking/sse/* (RealtimeCargoTrackingService.java, etc.)\n- All files under interfaces/handling/* (HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt.java, EventItemReader.java, EventItemWriter.java, FileProcessorJobListener.java, etc.)\n- All files under interfaces/tracking/* (Track.java, CargoTrackingViewAdapter.java)\n- FacesConfiguration.java - jakarta.enterprise.context\n- CoordinatesFactory.java - jakarta.enterprise.context, jakarta.inject\n\n### Pathfinder API (5 files)\n- GraphTraversalService.java\n- TransitPath.java\n- TransitPaths.java\n- TransitEdge.java\n- GraphDao.java\n\n### Test Files (10 files - except BookingServiceTest.java)\n- HandlingEventServiceTest.java - No Quarkus, just commented-out mocks\n- TestDataGenerator.java - Pure Jakarta\n- CargoTest.java - JUnit 5 only\n- ItineraryTest.java - JUnit 5 only\n- RouteSpecificationTest.java - JUnit 5 only\n- HandlingEventTest.java - JUnit 5 only\n- HandlingHistoryTest.java - JUnit 5 only\n- ExternalRoutingServiceTest.java - JUnit 5 only\n- CargoLifecycleScenarioTest.java - JUnit 5 only (commented out, but no Quarkus)\n\n---\n\n## CONFIGURATION FILES ANALYSIS\n\n### Standard Jakarta EE (NO changes needed):\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/web.xml** - Standard Jakarta Servlet 6.0\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/faces-config.xml** - Standard JSF 2.3\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/batch-jobs/EventFilesProcessorJob.xml** - Standard Jakarta Batch\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/resources/import.sql** - Standard SQL\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/resources/messages.properties** - Standard resource bundle\n\n---\n\n## SUMMARY STATISTICS\n\n- **Total Java files analyzed:** 106\n- **Files requiring Quarkus-to-Jakarta EE migration:** 15\n- **Files already using pure Jakarta EE:** 91\n\n### Migration Priority Breakdown:\n- **CRITICAL (must change):** 4 repository files (Panache dependency)\n- **HIGH (should change):** 7 files (JMS consumers, config injection)\n- **MEDIUM (nice to change):** 3 files (startup, scheduling, test data)\n- **LOW (optional):** 1 file (UI sort)\n\n### Key Quarkus Dependencies to Replace:\n1. **Panache ORM** (io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.panache.*) → Standard JPA EntityManager\n2. **Quarkus Scheduler** (io.quarkus.scheduler.Scheduled) → Jakarta EJB @Schedule\n3. **Quarkus Lifecycle** (io.quarkus.runtime.Startup/ShutdownEvent) → Jakarta @PostConstruct/@PreDestroy or @Startup\n4. **Quarkus Profiles** (io.quarkus.arc.profile.*) → Custom logic or environment variables\n5. **MicroProfile Config** (@ConfigProperty) → Already Jakarta EE 10 standard, but ensure proper setup\n\nThe good news is that **86% of the codebase is already pure Jakarta EE** and requires no changes!"}]}]},"paren