{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_014pcsMcDyK48pc5FsYR1PWY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Interesting - the error says it's expecting `https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jakartaee` but the schema says `https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence`. This is a known Payara 6 issue where the persistence XSD uses a different namespace. In Payara 6, the persistence namespace IS `https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/persistence` but the schema validator incorrectly expects `jakartaee`. Let me switch back to using the `jakartaee` namespace which is what Payara's schema validator expects:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3613,"cache_read_input_tokens":138803,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3613,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":430},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c9dd45e7-15fd-4879-bcb7-e7ebc835a938","uuid":"733f9e8b-05d1-4f06-be65-b96f10955231"}
